<%= section "Overview of topics" do %>

The topics section is where you add course materials, i.e. exercises and resources, in OST.<p>
   
<p>A topic represents 2 things in OST:</p>   
  (a) <strong>a topic is a group of related exercises and resources</strong>; and <br/>
  (b) <strong>a topic is a component of an assignment</strong>. <br/>
  
<p>The following chart explains more specifically how topics relate to assignments.</p>

<center>
<%= image_tag("topics_chart.png", {:border => 1, :width => "70%", :height => "70%", :title=>"create new topic"})%>
</center>

<p>How you organize your topics will depend on (a) the structure of your assignments and (b) the learning conditions set for your class, if any.</p>

<% end %>

